// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Cromley 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P87487943" "No no no. This is all wrong. The prophecy spoke not of a third. You are not the one who was meant for this ancient knowledge. Why is it that you are here instead of the chosen ones?"
// Answer Text :
"P1412693953" "What is this knowledge?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1246758557" "Nonsense. You come here seeking the knowledge and yet know nothing of it? Perhaps you are the fool that the prophecy mentions, but I always thought it was associated with the Selfish One. No matter, no matter. I shall tell you.<br><br>We have kept this knowledge for many lifetimes, beneath the waves where it was safe and secure until the time of the prophecy's fulfillment. Our task was to deliver the knowledge to the chosen ones. With this knowledge they will be equipped to deal with the trials that lie ahead of them. It is said that the knowledge bestows power that can only be used by the chosen ones, for they are to be tested by the powers that be."
// Answer Text :
"P2386647046" "Forget the chosen, I am worthy of this power."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1019271103" "Pah. The Prophecy warns against this. The power is too much for any one person to wield. This is why there are two chosen ones. The power gifted to one is balanced by the other. If the power is bestowed upon the wrong person, then it will do nothing, and the chosen will be consumed by eternal shadow. When bestowed upon the chosen ones, however, they have the power to bring great light into the world, or great darkness. It for them to decide which the world needs more."
// Answer Text :
"P3237292715" "You would gift such power to Flambeaux and Polar Shift?!"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P4169004627" "It is they who have been chosen. It is my duty as the keeper of the knowledge to bestow it upon those chosen by the prophecy and to no other."
// Answer Text :
"P547588267" "I can trust no other with such power, give it here, old man."
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P1569798013" "I will do no such thing. Oaths I have sworn prevent me, and demand that I defend the knowledge, with my very life if need be."
// Answer Text :
"P580894085" "I seek to prevent great evil. You would fight me?"
// Page InformationPage5 Text :
"P4284336886" "That is no longer up to me, my oaths demand it!"
// Answer Text :
"P2721087239" ""So be it." (Fight)"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3021123605" "You've checked Flambeaux's social network page again, just in case she posted updates. She did, but nothing of consequence. Once you find the cave she mentioned it shouldn't be very difficult to prove to the Legacy Chain that you are far more worthy for this power than Captain Braindead and Cold Shoulder. After all, the Legacy Chain doesn't mess around."
// AcceptString :
"P639845027" "Find the cave and take the mystical power for yourself"
// SendOffString :
"P1062695134" "You'll have to convince the Legacy Chain that you are more worthy than those two head cases. If they put up a fight, so much the better. Maybe a concussion would do Flambeaux some good."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2004191133" "Take the Mystic Power"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1317545013" "Flambeaux and Polar Shift are most likely already at the ritual. You'll have to hurry if you want to make sure you get this mystical power before them. If anyone stands in your way, you'll make them regret that decision."
// TaskTitle :
"P2294257271" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Flambeaux's Social Network Page</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Villigante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2289723181" "This is definitely the place. You can smell Flambeaux's perfume hanging in the air."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P4020913105" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Flambeaux's Social Network Page</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Well, mystical cosmic power was not yours to have, but at least you prevented Flambeaux and Polar Shift from getting it and immediately descending into darkness. If Sequester Cromley was telling the truth, then you did a great deed there. The mystical power was not guaranteed to be a force for good. If you couldn't wield it, then it is better that it not be chanced that it could wind up used for evil. You can't wait to get home and read Flambeaux's follow up post on her social network page. You highly doubt she'll mention the butt kicking you gave her, but at least you won't have to see pictures of her for awhile, what with that black eye you gave her."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1624023447" "Find Sequester Cromley and talk with him"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P890628734" "Polar Shift"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2756983888" "<shout>Okay, this is the place.  Flambeaux, could we get a little light?<em t=3>Flambeaux?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P944269117" "{HeroName}?  You're not allowed to be here!  The Legacy Chain won't trust us anymore if they think we brought you!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P1184200987" "{HeroName}, please stop fighting.  This ritual is very important!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P80585556" "Why... Why are you fighting us?"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2812811563" "Flambeaux!  FLAMBEAUX!!!  GET OVER HERE NOW!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1312390759" "I think {HeroName} is under some mental compulsion."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P855306552" "I'm... I'm hurt?  What... what are you... doing... {HeroName}?"
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P2212161453" "I'm sorry, but you'll need to be questioned back at the hospital."

