// Objective - ScriptLovedOneDefeated 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptLairBossAmbush 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P437540563" "Alan Westmore"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2959213025" "Once a Wolf Spider Huntsman in Arachnos, Alan Westmore found love and decided to flee from Lord Recluse's regime. Along his way he found a lot of like minded individuals, all of them wanting to redeem themselves for their service to the dictator of the Rogue Isles and head of the Arachnos  criminal organization."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2791976282" "<shout>NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3864644662" "{HeroName}! You monster! I'll kill you!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2547012120" "You killed her! You killed her! Why!? Tell me!!!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3269156606" "You call yourself a hero?! Look at what you've done! Look!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1066422620" "I can't... I can't fight anymore... just kill me... let me be with her... let me die..."
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P1014870455" "One day... someone like you... will do what you've done... to you... and yours...and we will be avenged..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
