"P1867567338" "Jump Bot Incinerator"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3565855875" "<shout>Destroy!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P485265676" "Destroy!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptAmbushDefeated2 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P4248461223" "Assault Jump Bot"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptAmbushDefeated3 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P758059038" "Captain"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2144752527" "<shout>The Jump Bots have failed, it's up to us!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3071390145" "Attack!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3301398297" "Captain Anderson"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P4067780330" "Captain Anderson claimed to have defected from the Sky Raiders, but his claims were an obvious cover to draw Longbow into a trap."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1059400768" "I cannot believe that even Overdrive fell into my trap. Duray was right, they are gullible."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1517861381" "Seems someone had the brains to question my loyalties. It took you long enough."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1222940169" "I can't believe you thought I would join Longbow! After what the government did to us!?"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3775064594" "I am so going to enjoy finishing you off!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P39258355" "Damn... You're good, {HeroName}... This isn't going as I planned!"

