// Objective - ScriptVillainBossDefeated 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P3116027099" "Defeat Captain Anderson"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P3469627621" "You rescued Overdrive from Captain Anderson's trap, though it cost the life of a senior Longbow commander, it saved the lives of dozens of Longbow personnel. You did what had to be done."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P694235662" "It turns out that Captain Anderson was working for the Sky Raiders all along. He tricked everyone, well, everyone but {HeroName}."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_VigToVil_SL4-5_Task_07 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - PrometheanSubnetSecurityAccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3875680973" ""Security Chief Jackson's Data Card"
// DetailString :
"P559081318" "This tiny credit card sized computer contains the security data you need to gain access to the facility's security terminals and override the Promethean's command protocols."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - SecurityTerminalDialogue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3024997479" "Welcome to Stroub Industries. With the proper security clearance this terminal provides access to all security systems within this facility."
// Answer Text :
"P1688965117" "Look for information about the demonstration"
// Answer Text :
"P4203874432" "Access the secure Promethean subnet"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1731292800" "Today's demonstration is of the new Promethean android. This technological advancement is equipped with cutting edge AI and superior adaptive construction, making it a valuable addition to any city's municipal maintenance system, especially in particularly dangerous built up urban centers that still dot the globe in the aftermath of the Rikti invasion.<br><br>The Promethean comes equipped with a particle beam cutter, enhanced carbon fiber <i>muscle</i> giving it incredible lifting, hauling, and gripping strength, and a self repair system to eliminate all but the most critical maintenance support. It truly is an automated unit that can provide construction, demolition, and rescue work anywhere in the world.<br><br>Today's closed doors demonstration is for investment opportunities of this exciting new product to be shipped within the next year."
// Page AccessSubnetDenied Text :
"P1627697515" "I'm sorry, but you do not possess the required security permissions for that action. Please contact Security Chief Jackson to request clearance."
// Answer Text :
"P3774462160" "I'll go find Jackson and get clearance"
// Page AccessSubnetPermitted Text :
"P4035125290" "Secure subnet accessed. Please enter your command."
// Answer Text :
"P2878077032" "Override and uplink to the internal network"
// Page ConfirmOverride Text :
"P4177467697" "Override completed.<br><br>..........<br><br>..........<br><br>..........<br><br>...<br><br>Uplink Completed.<br><br>Ready for command."
// Answer Text :
"P3829177755" "Set Promethean to hostile stance"
// Page SetBerserkMode Text :
"P4245856589" "Hostile stance sent to Promethean android.<br><br>..........<br><br>Command accepted.<br><br>Incoming update.<br><br>Promethean has detect 27 hostile targets.<br><br>Engaging."
// Answer Text :
"P1050557039" "Destroy the terminal"
// Page SelfDestruct Text :
"P2583298220" "<color orange>It doesn't take much for you to reduce the terminal to scrap metal</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P3669323332" "Now to come to the rescue."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3957481571" "From those reams of scientific nonsense it looks like the Promethean android is a pretty rugged robot, it's also carrying a particle beam cutter, supposedly for construction and demolition work. You know that it will just be used as a weapon against innocent populations once the umpti-umpth villain realizes that the government has built them an army of robotic killing machines for them to exploit and turn on the masses. This ends before it starts."
// AcceptString :
"P1745728365" "Turn the Promethean on its creators to show them the error of their ways"
// SendOffString :
"P1279621599" "The first step is going to be getting access to the facility's security terminal. From there you should be able to access the Promethean's subnet and issue it new commands. The trick is going to be getting access to the security terminal, but you're pretty sure someone on staff will have the access codes you need, it's just a matter of making them help you."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2291385311" "Sabotage the Promethean Demonstration"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2405071627" "Finding the chief of security will be a good first move. With him out of commission nobody else should bother you. He'll also know everyone at the demonstration and how you can get access to the security terminal."
// TaskTitle :
"P6852411" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Reams Of Scientific Gibberish</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P4155744065" "Dr. Stroub has begun the demonstration. With all eyes on him now is the perfect time to sneak into the facility and begin your plan."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3834825733" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Reams Of Scientific Gibberish</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Not bad for a day's work. The Promethean android was destroyed and Dr. Stroub was disgraced. Better still, that little demonstration you put together of how badly that technology could be twisted to serve a villain should dissuade anyone from investing in that kind of research for years to come."
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P1186017415" "The Promethean's regenerative armor has kicked in."
// Script Variable FloaterMessage :
"P3155022497" "The Promethean is regenerating!"
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P561454964" "The Promethean's automated repair system has activated."
// Script Variable FloaterMessage :
"P3541390144" "The Promethean is repairing itself!"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1847749181" "Override the Promethean security protocols."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptEnterMission 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P840709866" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Welcome, everyone. I'm Professor Stroub, team leader of the Promethean Project, and owner of Stroub Industries. <t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>I can tell that you are all interested in getting underway with the demonstration, so let's just jump into it!<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Today, I present to you the Promethean, a new class of hyperadvanced android.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>However, the Promethean is not just any other android. <t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>The Promethean is programmed with thousands of routines and subroutines, intended to mimic human cognitive reasoning.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>It is equipped with more than just a human form, it carries all the tools it will ever need within its chassis.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>If it needs a tool it doesn't have, it can build it!<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>With the Promethean in your city, you won't ever have to worry about the city's municipal infrastructure breaking down!<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>But why just take my word for it? I am biased, I built the dang thing after all.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>How about I show you what the Promethean can do."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P680199858" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>As you can see, the Promethean is built using advanced carbon fiber and adaptive nanotubes.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>In plain speak, he's made out of some high tech space age indestructible stuff, or very well near it.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>His strength, as you can see here is provided not by archaic hydraulics, but by advanced nanotube muscles. <t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>This guy can lift a tank with one hand, and rescue a kitten with the other."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2749545896" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Now here's a fun bit. Ha ha, see, he can even be used for entertainment.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Truly the Promethean is more than just a feat of engineering unmatched in the world today, he's an inspiration for a new tomorrow.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Production for the Promethean is scheduled for next year. All we need is the support of people who share the same vision as I do.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>A vision of a better tomorrow, today."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P3383307626" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Wait... whoa there boy. Carla, what's going on?<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Promethean... No! NO! Stand down. Minor technical problem everyone.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Carla! What's going on?! Send the override signal, get it under control. Whoa!<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Ok, everyone, while Carla is working out the problem... Ok, everyone out, it's out of control! Quickly!<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.2 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>Carla! We need to get out of here now!<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBirck>Seal the demonstration area. Call SERAPH and get someone down here ASAP."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1171783381" "<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>This is channel eight news reporting live on a situation inside the Stroub Industries robotics testing facility.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>It appears that a demonstration has gone awry and has threatened the lives of at least two dozen people here.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>Footage recorded by smart phone from people inside the demonstration has already made it online.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor FireBrick>From what it looks like, and here's a clip, the technology is an android and. Oh my! It's going berserk.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>Fortunately for Professor Stroub, {HeroName} was in the area and is on the scene.<t=5 caption x= 0.2 y=0.4 d=4><scale 1.75><color white><bgcolor SlateBlue>We'll have more on this story as it developes. Back to you, Bob."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3487105970" "Security Chief Jackson"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1514650256" "<shout>Keep your eyes peeled. We got a report that someone's snooping around the premises.<em>I don't want any mishaps today, there are guys in there that make more money in an hour than all of us annually."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3510637035" "There's the intruder!"

